<Author>Tomzie
<Content>Great average hotel but very noisy! The service at the hotel was great! We have booked true internet and everything went fine. Even when we arrived later than 00 pm the staff was still friendly and helpful. The rooms are fine and clean, but very noisy! It was hot in Berlin and if you did open the windows you could hear the highway. Airco would be a great +++ It was noisy but the beds are very good so I got a good sleep. The bathroom is to small, certainly if you are whit two people in the room. Breakfast was also fine, great avarage + hotel, great value! Easy to reach with public transport. So it's not the grand luxe but the service is very good. Fine, small hotel. It would go back to this hotel 
